videos.title: Brain Stem (Basic Concepts) part 1
videos.description:
1)	Parts of the brainstem. (00:00...3:46min)
2)	Location and main functions of cerebral as well as cerebellar peduncles (3:47...6:20min)

c.	Sixth nerve (abducens nerve), Seventh nerve (facial nerve) and Eighth nerve (vestibulocochlear nerve). (19:11...24:20min)

6)	Structural conversion of spinal cord to brainstem, cranial nerve nuclei, supplementary grey areas and reticular formation (42:42...58:10min)
